Reasoning: 
1. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on developing a planner to guide robots in assembly using translational motion. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed planner finds the optimal solution by permuting and evaluating possible assembly sequences, which involves AI techniques. 
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The input to the planner includes mesh models of the objects, which may involve computer vision techniques. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with planning and controlling the assembly process, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics): The paper may involve graphics techniques for visualizing the assembly process and the objects involved.
